   "source": [
    "# Phase B Session 3: Full SU-HBO Run\n",
    "## Stepwise Utility-guided Hierarchical Bayesian Optimization\n",
    "\n",
    "**Goal**: Run the full SU-HBO algorithm to find optimal architecture.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Data**: 90% CIFAR-10 (excluding Session 2 calibration indices)\n",
    "**Algorithm**: SU-HBO with utility function validated in Session 2\n",
    "\n",
    "**Session 2 Result**: Spearman r = 0.81 > 0.70 ✓"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Setup"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%cd /kaggle/working\n",
